Here is a sample healthy meal plan for today:

Breakfast:

* 1 cup nonfat plain Greek yogurt (100 calories)
* 1/2 cup mixed berries (60 calories)
* 1/2 cup high-fiber cereal (100 calories)
* 1 hard-boiled egg (78 calories)

Total: 348 calories

Lunch:

* 4 oz grilled chicken breast (120 calories)
* 1 cup cooked quinoa (150 calories)
* 1 cup steamed broccoli (55 calories)
* 1 medium apple (95 calories)

Total: 470 calories

Dinner:

* 4 oz grilled salmon (180 calories)
* 1 cup cooked brown rice (110 calories)
* 1 cup sautéed spinach (20 calories)
* 1/2 cup roasted bell peppers (60 calories)

Total: 470 calories

Snacks:

* 1 medium apple (95 calories)
* 1 oz almonds (160 calories)

Total: 255 calories

Total daily calorie intake: 1838 calories

This meal plan provides approximately 45% of your daily calorie needs and is balanced to include protein, healthy fats, fiber, and a variety of vitamins and minerals. It is important to stay hydrated by drinking plenty of water throughout the day.
